Description:
Following the carriage trail, you arrive at Lake Senenthia, usually this lake is always full of locals who fish, trade or perform daily activities, but today it seems that no one is around.

So it is not often that you can explore the lake thoroughly without being disturbed.

You can also fish or search for magic shards.
DescriptionAction: This morning the lake is all for you.
